text: Fedikovella is a genus of sea snails, deep-sea limpets, marine gastropod mollusks in the family Cocculinidae. ==Species== Species within the genus Fedikovella include: * Fedikovella beanii (Dall, 1882) * Fedikovella caymanensis Moskalev, 1976 ==References== ==External links== Category:Cocculinidae Category:Gastropod genera
title: Fedikovella
